episodes.title: Leah Remini Mourns Mike Rinder, Scientology and the Aftermath Co-Host, Dead at 69
episodes.description: Leah Remini remembers her 'Scientology and the Aftermath' co-host, Mike Rinder, who died Sunday, in a lengthy tribute on X. He was 69. The friends and former Scientology members also shared a podcast together, 'Fair Game.'
